Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Inflation dips slightly
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w7w2
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 1 Mar 1981
Inflation rate growth under zero - but the new figure misses out on oil price increases. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less